snippet.title: Quake Sewer Jam - Burnham - Waterdeep Junction
snippet.description:
Waterdeep Junction is my entry for the Quake Sewer Jam that took place during the month of August, 2019! 11 maps were made by 11 mappers, featuring a variety of takes on the sewer theme! Enjoy!

For my map, my goal was to make a short, hub-and-spoke design with spooky encounters and some light narrative threads. It is my second solo Quake map and third Quake map overall. Let me know what you think if you play it!

Download the map pack here:
http://quaketastic.com/files/single_player/sewerjam.zip

Map pack trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZJ35n58dTyQ&feature=youtu.be

This jam was organized and run by Andrew Yoder (thank you!)
https://andrewyoderdesign.blog/2019/09/02/the-sewer-jam-is-out/
https://www.youtube.com/user/Mclogenog

Func_Msgboard post: http://www.celephais.net/board/view_thread.php?id=61769

Join the Quake Mapping Discord and you can be a mapper too!
https://discord.gg/yah6d4

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/NCBurnham
